Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須去書店  把書取回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,春日君你偷了佐伯同學的體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不想被說出去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看今天的氣氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都沒聽你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還不都怨你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,趁這個機會不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那本書買回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,預定的那本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸我也想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,借我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒  還沒買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,高男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,自行車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我給忘在書店了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子去書店了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,高男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  孩他媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,高男也到了這個年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有他自己的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,已經 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經 墮落了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,仲村 肯定會說出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能不抖出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,豈止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還不知道會做出什麼更過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 為什麼
